sections.Trivia:
- This episode is a sequel to Ramen So Good, It's to Die For.
- The names of the suspects come from types of ramen[1]:
- Atsuko Tonda (頓田 温子) comes from tonkotsu ramen (豚骨ラーメン);
- Yuna Shōno (荘野 由奈) comes from shōyu ramen (醤油ラーメン) and abura soba (油そば), a type of noodle;
- Sōsuke Mizushina (水科 宗輔) comes from miso ramen (味噌ラーメン) and shina soba (支那そば), another name for ramen noodles;
- Osamu Nakanishi (仲西 修) comes from shio ramen (塩ラーメン) and chūka soba (中華そば), another name for ramen noodles.
